== Devache Kakutichem Rupkar - Divine Mercy Image ==

=== Devache Kakutichem Rupkar ===

1931 vea vorsa Fevrerache 22ver Polant ghavan Kakutsor Jezu St. Faustinak
dixtti podtta. Ti he porim boroita;"Eke sanjer, hanv mojea kuddan astana, 
havem Jezuk eka dovenful angvostrant pollelo. Ek hat ubarlolo adhinvecheak besanv ani dusro ordear dovorlolo.  
Tachea angvostrantlean, don uzvaddachem kirnam bhair sortalim,  Ek, tambddem ani dusrem dovsar.  Hanv oginch 
nialltalim.  Eke vatten mojer bhirant suttleli ani dusre vatten, vhodd koxealkai bhogleli.  Thoddea
vellar Jezun maka sanglem. "

"Tuvem pollelaim tea pormonnem chitar(paint) ani sokla him utram borai JEZU HANV TUJER PATIETAN, Maka zai 
tea rupkarak poilo tumchea kopelant man dilolo ani uprant soglea sonvsarant (Pustok47)

