=== Hea Rupkarachi Somzoni ===

St Faustinachea konfesoran tichem lagim maglem, Suan Jezu kodde vichar mhunn  heam 2 kirnanchi somzonni.  Tinnem Jezu lagim
vinchartoch.  Tannem heporim somzonni dili.  "Kirnam hea rupkaracher dakoitat rogot ani udok jem Mhoje kakutintlea thavantlem vhanvlem, jedna 
Khursar Mhojem Khontiborit Kalliz vidarlem.  Him dovsar kirnam dakhoitat udok jem duta amcho otmo ani tambddin kirnam-Rogot jem vortovta
otmeanchem jivit.  Him Kirnam samballtat munxeak Mhojea Bapachea ragantlo.  Suki ho zo kirnanchea asrea khal jieta, kiteak thium kednanch Devache niticho hat pavchona." (Pustok 299)

Hanv munxeank ek aidon ditam, zache vorvim sogleamnin kakutiche zhorixim vocheunk zai kurpa gheunk.  Tem aidon vortouta hem rupkar(Chitar) ani tacher hem boroup asum : JEZU HANV TUJER PATIENTAM (Pustok 327)

Hanv bhasaitam konn jea rupkarak man dita kednanch emkonddant vechonam. Tea bhiar, hea sanvsarant, odik korun mornnachea vellar dusmanancher oit vortole. Hanvunch taka samballtolom Mozo Onod zalelea porim (Pustok 48 )

