=== Devache Kakuticho Ters ===

Devache kakutichea tersacho oramb :  1935 vea vorsa Setembrache 13ver St. Faustinan ek Boddvo pollelo, Devachi nit korunk pattoilolo.  Vis ani ghoddghodde tachea hatant aslele.  Devachea ragacheo khunna mhunnun tika kollon ailem. Devan pattoilo mhunn sonvsarak, odik korun eka kherit ganvank khast launcheak. Tea bori ti khotkhotit magnnim korunk lagli.  Tinnem Boddvea laghim kakut kor mhun prarthun maglem.  Punn, tika dison ailem tichim magnnim Devacho raag palounk folladik nhoi mhunn.  Tednam sogli trinidad tika dixtti poddli.  Ti tea porzollan soglich guspoli.  Tea borobar, tinnem him utram aikolim "Sasnnachea Bapa, hanv Tuca bheittoitam amchea ani soglea sounvsaracheam patkamchea farikponna bhov khatir, Tujea Bhou Mogalla Putrachi ani Amchea Dhonia ani Soddvonnara, Jezu Kristachi Kudd ani Rogot, ani Otmo ani Devponn.  Tachea bhou dukhest koxtam khatir, amchi ani soglea Sonvsarachi Kakut kor." Heam utramnim tinnem sonvsarachea salvasanvam khatir Devak ulo marunk suru kelem.  Ani ojeapanchem ojeap !  Hea magnneachi podvi itli ki Boddvea laghim annik khast launk goddona zalem." ( Pustok 474, 475)

Dusrea disa Kopelant bhitor sortana him utram tinnem aikolim :- "Jitle pavtti tum kopelant bhitor sortai, title pavtti mhunn havem kal magnnem xikoilam tem.  "Tinnem hem magnnem mhunnlea uprant, novena za aikoli sangun - "Hem magnnem Devacho rag palounk chodd folladik.  Tum tersachea kontar mhunn he porim. "


